# .gitignore — Cooperative Society Management Portal

# ── Backend ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# clasp credentials (contains your Google OAuth token — NEVER commit this)
.clasprc.json
backend/.clasp.json

# ── Frontend ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Do NOT ignore config.js (it should only contain the GAS URL — no secrets)
# If you add sensitive values to config.js in future, add it here.

# ── OS / Editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── Legacy GAS template files (no longer needed in the frontend) ──────────────
# These remain in the root directory for reference but are not part of the
# static frontend. They are superseded by frontend/ versions.
# Uncomment below if you want to exclude them from Git tracking:
# *.html
# *.gs
